to fix a past fracture.

03:01.849 --> 03:04.090
Could be
a helpful identifier.

03:04.185 --> 03:05.925
Very good,
Mr. Nigel-Murray.

03:06.020 --> 03:09.763
While I have your attention
and affection, there’s something
that I’d like to say.

03:09.899 --> 03:12.265
Can you speak while working?
Of course.

03:12.360 --> 03:16.399
As you may be aware,
I am currently participating
in Alcoholics Anonymous,

03:16.489 --> 03:20.653
