- Welcome to the Pine Tree Manor.

09:07.506 --> 09:11.624
It would
more properly be called
the Cedar Siding Manor.

09:11.719 --> 09:13.584
Right. Uh, F.B.|.
Special Agent Seeley Booth.

09:13.679 --> 09:15.886
This here’s my colleague,
Dr. Temperance Brennan.

09:15.973 --> 09:17.759
You must be here because of the myth guy.

09:17.850 --> 09:19.841
I’m Randy Shepard.
I own the place.

09:19.935 --> 09:22.051
- Is it true what we’re hearing?
