09:22.146 --> 09:25.638
That something got the guy—
out in the woods, something... horrible.

09:25.733 --> 09:28.440
- And how’d you hear about that?
- From me.

09:28.569 --> 09:30.480
Who are you?
I’m Melissa Lawson.

09:30.571 --> 09:33.278
- Melissa’s our activities coordinator.
- What does that mean?

09:33.365 --> 09:36.732
Fishing, hikes, bird-watching,
nature trails, hunting.

09:36.827 --> 09:39.443
Mr. Coleman sort of
monopolized Melissa
the three days he was here.

09:39.538 --> 09:41.995
He was filming an episode
of that show of his.

09:42.082 --> 09:43.788
To debunk the chupacabra?

09:43.876 --> 09:46.333
- Yeah. And it got him.
- We’ve had sightings.

09:46.420 --> 09:49.332
People used to come from all over
just to get a glimpse of one.

09:50.424 --> 09:52.415
- What’s it look like?
- Oh.

09:57.514 --> 10:00.881
- [Cell Phone Rings]
- Hello.

10:00.976 --> 10:03.558
So, I’ve analyzed
those dermal cells
we found on the remains.

10:03.645 --> 10:05.852
Tums out they are skin,
